2d overhead style game 
space themed
some sort of disaster happens and enemies spawn at increassing rates until you get the time reverse activated
different rooms
different doors will bring you to different rooms at different points in time
Ship attempting to travel across time but it goes wrong and now the ship is split into different points in time of the ship's history and future.


ULTIMATE GOAL
to fix the ship

gathering and making the correct componets to fix the ship at the correct time
